<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Digital Experience (Synthetics) on Splunk Observability Cloud Workshops</title><link>https://splunk.github.io/observability-workshop/pt-br/splunk4rookies/observability-cloud-short/6-synthetics/</link><description>Recent content in Digital Experience (Synthetics) on Splunk Observability Cloud Workshops</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>pt-BR</language><atom:link href="https://splunk.github.io/observability-workshop/pt-br/splunk4rookies/observability-cloud-short/6-synthetics/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>1. Dashboard de Synthetics</title><link>https://splunk.github.io/observability-workshop/pt-br/splunk4rookies/observability-cloud-short/6-synthetics/1-synthetics-dashboard/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://splunk.github.io/observability-workshop/pt-br/splunk4rookies/observability-cloud-short/6-synthetics/1-synthetics-dashboard/</guid><description>&lt;section class="exercise"&gt;
&lt;header class="exercise__bar"&gt;
&lt;span class="exercise__bar-icon" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/&gt;&lt;circle cx="12" cy="12" r="6"/&gt;&lt;circle cx="12" cy="12" r="2"/&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="exercise__bar-label"&gt;Exercício&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="exercise__bar-divider" aria-hidden="true"&gt;·&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="exercise__bar-title"&gt;Encontrar uma execução com falha em Synthetics&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/header&gt;
&lt;div class="exercise__panel"&gt;
&lt;div class="exercise__body"&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;No Splunk Observability Cloud, no menu principal, clique em &lt;strong&gt;Digital Experience → Synthetics tests&lt;/strong&gt;. Clique em &lt;strong&gt;All&lt;/strong&gt; ou &lt;strong&gt;Browser tests&lt;/strong&gt; para ver a lista de testes ativos.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Durante nossa investigação na seção de RUM, encontramos um problema com a Transaction &lt;strong&gt;Place Order&lt;/strong&gt;. Vamos ver se também conseguimos confirmar isso pelo teste de Synthetics.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Na caixa &lt;strong&gt;Search&lt;/strong&gt;, digite &lt;strong&gt;[NAME OF WORKSHOP]&lt;/strong&gt; para filtrar os testes deste workshop.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>2. Detalhe do teste de Synthetics</title><link>https://splunk.github.io/observability-workshop/pt-br/splunk4rookies/observability-cloud-short/6-synthetics/2-synthetics-detail/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://splunk.github.io/observability-workshop/pt-br/splunk4rookies/observability-cloud-short/6-synthetics/2-synthetics-detail/</guid><description>&lt;section class="exercise"&gt;
&lt;header class="exercise__bar"&gt;
&lt;span class="exercise__bar-icon" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/&gt;&lt;circle cx="12" cy="12" r="6"/&gt;&lt;circle cx="12" cy="12" r="2"/&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="exercise__bar-label"&gt;Exercício&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="exercise__bar-divider" aria-hidden="true"&gt;·&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="exercise__bar-title"&gt;Inspecionar o playback do teste&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/header&gt;
&lt;div class="exercise__panel"&gt;
&lt;div class="exercise__body"&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Agora estamos olhando para o resultado de um único Synthetic Browser Test.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;figure class="figure"&gt;
 &lt;div class="figure__inner"&gt;
 &lt;img src="../images/synth-waterfall.png" alt="waterfall" loading="lazy" decoding="async"&gt;
 &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Por padrão, Splunk Synthetics fornece capturas de tela e gravação em vídeo do teste. Isso é útil para depurar problemas. Você pode ver, por exemplo, o carregamento lento de imagens grandes, a renderização lenta de uma página etc.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Use o mouse para rolar para a esquerda e para a direita pela filmstrip e ver como o site estava sendo renderizado durante a execução do teste.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>3. Synthetics para APM</title><link>https://splunk.github.io/observability-workshop/pt-br/splunk4rookies/observability-cloud-short/6-synthetics/3-synthetics-to-apm/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://splunk.github.io/observability-workshop/pt-br/splunk4rookies/observability-cloud-short/6-synthetics/3-synthetics-to-apm/</guid><description>&lt;section class="exercise"&gt;
&lt;header class="exercise__bar"&gt;
&lt;span class="exercise__bar-icon" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/&gt;&lt;circle cx="12" cy="12" r="6"/&gt;&lt;circle cx="12" cy="12" r="2"/&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="exercise__bar-label"&gt;Exercício&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="exercise__bar-divider" aria-hidden="true"&gt;·&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="exercise__bar-title"&gt;Ir de Synthetics para APM&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/header&gt;
&lt;div class="exercise__panel"&gt;
&lt;div class="exercise__body"&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;No waterfall, encontre uma entrada que começa com &lt;strong&gt;POST checkout&lt;/strong&gt;. Se você não vir essa entrada, volte e selecione outro resultado com falha na página &lt;strong&gt;Run results&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;figure class="figure"&gt;
 &lt;div class="figure__inner"&gt;
 &lt;img src="../images/run-results-place-order.png" alt="Place Order" loading="lazy" decoding="async"&gt;
 &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Clique em &lt;strong&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;strong&gt;(1)&lt;/strong&gt; para abrir a seção de metadados. Observe os metadados coletados e repare no header &lt;strong&gt;server-timing&lt;/strong&gt; em &lt;strong&gt;Response Headers&lt;/strong&gt;. Esse header é o que nos permite correlacionar a execução do teste com um trace de back-end.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Clique no link azul &lt;span class="inline-icon"&gt;&lt;svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path d="M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71"/&gt;&lt;path d="M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71"/&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;APM&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;strong&gt;(2)&lt;/strong&gt; na linha &lt;strong&gt;POST checkout&lt;/strong&gt; do waterfall.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;figure class="figure"&gt;
 &lt;div class="figure__inner"&gt;
 &lt;img src="../images/apm-trace.png" alt="APM trace" loading="lazy" decoding="async"&gt;
 &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>4. Detector de Synthetics</title><link>https://splunk.github.io/observability-workshop/pt-br/splunk4rookies/observability-cloud-short/6-synthetics/4-synthetics-detector/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://splunk.github.io/observability-workshop/pt-br/splunk4rookies/observability-cloud-short/6-synthetics/4-synthetics-detector/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;Como você pode executar esses testes 24/7, eles são uma ferramenta ideal para receber avisos cedo quando seus testes estão falhando ou começando a demorar mais do que o SLA combinado, em vez de descobrir por redes sociais ou sites de uptime.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;figure class="figure"&gt;
 &lt;div class="figure__inner"&gt;
 &lt;img src="../images/social-media-post.png" alt="Social media" loading="lazy" decoding="async"&gt;
 &lt;/div&gt;
 
&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Para evitar que isso aconteça, vamos detectar se nosso teste está levando mais de 50 segundos.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>5. Criar Detector</title><link>https://splunk.github.io/observability-workshop/pt-br/splunk4rookies/observability-cloud-short/6-synthetics/5-create-detector/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://splunk.github.io/observability-workshop/pt-br/splunk4rookies/observability-cloud-short/6-synthetics/5-create-detector/</guid><description>&lt;section class="exercise"&gt;
&lt;header class="exercise__bar"&gt;
&lt;span class="exercise__bar-icon" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/&gt;&lt;circle cx="12" cy="12" r="6"/&gt;&lt;circle cx="12" cy="12" r="2"/&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="exercise__bar-label"&gt;Exercício&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="exercise__bar-divider" aria-hidden="true"&gt;·&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="exercise__bar-title"&gt;Receber alertas&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/header&gt;
&lt;div class="exercise__panel"&gt;
&lt;div class="exercise__body"&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Vá para &lt;strong&gt;Digital Experience → Synthetics tests&lt;/strong&gt; no menu principal.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Selecione o teste do workshop &lt;strong&gt;[NAME OF WORKSHOP]&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Clique no teste.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Clique no botão &lt;button class="btn-inline" type="button"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Create Detector&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/button&gt; no topo da página:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Altere os critérios de alerta para que a métrica seja &lt;strong&gt;Run Duration&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;strong&gt;(1)&lt;/strong&gt; (em vez de Uptime) e a condição seja &lt;strong&gt;Static Threshold&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Defina o &lt;strong&gt;Trigger threshold&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;strong&gt;(2)&lt;/strong&gt; para algo em torno de &lt;code&gt;50000&lt;/code&gt; ms.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Defina &lt;strong&gt;Split by location&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;strong&gt;(3)&lt;/strong&gt; como &lt;strong&gt;No&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Observe que agora há uma linha de triângulos vermelhos e brancos aparecendo abaixo dos picos no gráfico.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Os triângulos vermelhos indicam que o detector encontrou seu teste acima do limite definido, e o triângulo branco indica que o resultado voltou para baixo do limite. Cada triângulo vermelho disparará um alerta.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;div class="callout callout--warning"&gt;&lt;span class="callout__icon" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path d="M10.29 3.86 1.82 18a2 2 0 0 0 1.71 3h16.94a2 2 0 0 0 1.71-3L13.71 3.86a2 2 0 0 0-3.42 0z"/&gt;&lt;line x1="12" y1="9" x2="12" y2="13"/&gt;&lt;line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12.01" y2="17"/&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;p class="callout__title"&gt;Não adicionaremos um destinatário nem ativaremos o detector, pois não queremos inundar seu e-mail com alertas.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>